Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:32.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...One Hundred Poets...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and kite flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:37.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I've never actually seen someone do those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:38.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.44,0:02:42.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,These days, it's dangerous with \Nstuff like electric lines and cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I just watched TV and read books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,After those first three busy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:47.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I did those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:53.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I enjoyed badminton, One Hundred\NPoets, and Pin the Tail on the Donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Doesn't match your image.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My family follows western customs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but our relatives in the country are more traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We wore kimonos and went \Nto the temple on New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:05.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and I had fun with my cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An omnipotent god...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Way more Japanese than I am!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More traditional than my family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:12.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, why Pin the Tail on the Donkey?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:14.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In One Hundred Poets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...they're all 31 syllable poems, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:17.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:19.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You read out the first verse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:21.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and look for the card with the rest of the poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:22.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You must have skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:23.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm just a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:28.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The expert snatch up the cards in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:29.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:33.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can't stand playing a game that\Nmakes you feel like you're studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.63,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,People like you who view mental games as a\Nchore are why Japan's going down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't they use One \NHundred Poets for like a card battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:42.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You could summon a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:44.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Think there was a Semimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Semimaru uses a shining attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:48.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Ono no Komachi uses a lovely strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that sound fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:50.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Back to your world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:55.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't more physical games \Nhave helped you lose weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It was those stupid rice cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Rice cakes are loaded with calories, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:02.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,One as big as a matchbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:05.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...is equivalent to a whole bowl of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Which means that Kagami's eating \Na bowl of rice with each bite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:08.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You also ate rice cakes, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:14.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My mom's gone, so I've rarely \Nhad zoni soup and that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't really eat rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:18.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,With zoni soup, sweet red bean \Nsoup, soy flour rice cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,There are so many fun ways to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:27.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's gonna lose to \Nthe rice cakes again next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:32.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What do you have to eat for New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...instead of rice cakes, Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:36.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Stuff like pizza and pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:39.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Our year starts with raw pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:43.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My dad cleans out the pasta \Nmachine at the end of every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:44.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:47.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That thing rusts if you don't use it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you use it without cleaning it first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...the pasta ends up all black and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So we clean it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:56.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and make pasta and pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sounds very thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, Kagami's house probably orders\Npizza and their pasta consists of cup noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,More like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We don't have pizza or pasta on New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:07.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It doesn't go with traditional foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:10.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sure it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:13.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It goes great with roast chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's a traditional New Year's food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:17.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Under western traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What did you have for New Year's, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:27.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Your family sounds all wealthy and western...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:30.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so you probably didn't have \Ntraditional stuff or rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:32.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Maybe you had like a full course French dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I ate traditional foods...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and I was unable to bite through a rice cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and it stretched like whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.96,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with this walking pillar \Nto elements of turn-ons?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Rice cake goes whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:49.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But New Year's goes by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:50.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Winter break goes by fast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be a long vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:57.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but after cleaning, writing \NNew Year's cards, and homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you don't have much time to relax, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:00.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You didn't do New Year's cards this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And you copied my homework yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Did you have your first dream of the year, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:10.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Isn't it supposed to be a good\Nomen if you dream about certain things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:11.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:16.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Usually, it's one: Mt. Fuji, two: hawk, three: eggplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Officially, you would add...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:22.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...four: fan, five: tobacco, six: blind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:25.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It goes all the way up to six!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:25.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Who ever dreams about that kind of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:29.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What kind of dream would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And why a blind man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:31.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Pretty much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:32.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Do you have to dream about all of those at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If all of those showed up in \Nyour dreams, you'd be really blessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but I believe that just one will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:45.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I thought you would have to dream about\Na hawk twice and an eggplant three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:46.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And quite frankly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Who really remembers what they dream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:53.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,People who care about that stuff are\Nhaving way too much fun with New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In my first dream this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:07:00.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I opened my shoe locker to find my shoes missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So I had no choice but to take\Nshoes from someone else's open locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but the size was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:11.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I looked up the meaning of this dream in\Nthe encyclopedia for dream fortune telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and it said that it's a sign I am \Npursuing skills useful to society...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:18.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but it will take a while before I accomplish that goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:22.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The shoes apparently represent societal standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:23.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Cheesecake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:26.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...pretty ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's like I kinda understand, but kinda not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:36.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Another person was goofing off on the stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...during the coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:41.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't they realize they're representing Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Makes you wonder why they even bother going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:49.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to go to a \Nboring coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:52.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this girl's gonna grow up to be a bad person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:56.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What are you guys going to wear to your ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:59.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Might as well go with a long-sleeve kimono...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:02.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:05.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,My dad's probably going to \Nhave me wear a long-sleeve kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:06.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can see him doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:08.27,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:08.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When you wear one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:12.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you'd look more like a little kid going to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:13.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:14.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hope ya had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Cousin Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:18.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, my husband was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:21.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And a lot happens during New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:24.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, and my sister had a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She's got a weak body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It definitely wasn't because I didn't\Ngive her any New Year's allowance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:34.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only a cop would reveal what she was\Nreally thinking before I've said a thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A One Hundred Poets tournament \Nis currently underway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and it's been one crazy ride so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:44.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What did you do on New Year's when you were a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:45.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, I did all kinds of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:49.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:51.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:55.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:56.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:56.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:56.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:57.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She really just goes with the flow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never heard her say anything serious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess I outgrew my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:14.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's always cooped up \Nunder the kotatsu these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:15.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.09,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kotatsus are so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:21.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Going to the bathroom's a pain though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:22.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But you shouldn't say that so loudly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:28.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But we have a surefire way to \Nget a person out of a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:29.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If you stay under the kotatsu too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...you'll get stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So your dad doesn't need a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,He likes them as much as the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:40.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's just like a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,'Cause we've both fallen asleep \Ntogether under the kotatsu before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But they say that you'll catch a\Ncold if you fall asleep under a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:48.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:51.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So we turn it off once someone notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:55.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's like a mix of heaven and hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like right before you turn it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and after you turn it off, it feels even colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I totally know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And doesn't it really suck when \Nyou get out of bed in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:10.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,While we're at it, it's totally freezing after you\Nget undressed and before you get in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But not enough to make you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You might slip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:18.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And doesn't it suck when you need to go\Nthe bathroom in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:19.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I hate that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:20.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:21.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is our stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:25.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And the trip from the bus to the classroom is also hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's almost Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It always gets a lot more exciting this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:36.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It kinda tickles me how everyone \Ncan get so worked up every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Having someone special on this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:40.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and confessing your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...and having them reciprocated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.88,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...is a beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're such a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I just see it as a conspiracy by the chocolate industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:54.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you could say it's \Nalso a special time of year for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:57.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They have a sale on the unsold chocolate afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:10:59.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I'm looking for chocolate to use in making my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And you, you have no dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Money can't buy love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,At least, that's what they like to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but isn't Valentine chocolate a\Nway of showing love through money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:12.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I guess someone who's only\Nexperienced love in games has some harsh views.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:18.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, in games, it's all about upping\Nyour relationship level before the day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:22.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I don't do anything special for Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:23.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guys dream too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nobody managed to trigger the Kagami flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm super popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:35.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,When you talk about flags and relationship levels...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...I seriously get worried about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:40.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can't limit yourself to events in games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:44.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I can't stand those narrow-minded people\Nwho don't know what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Lately, events only take a few hours in game time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:52.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so Valentine's Day is usually over in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:57.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But this year, I'm planning on \Ngiving chocolate to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:58.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Someone playing the same online game as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:03.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A friend from your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're giving it to him in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:09.06,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm not actually going to meet the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It'll be in-game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:14.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Since the characters are still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Does that even count?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So you just meant a game character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:20.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,How dare you insult my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:24.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We're married in-game, and my character's male.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:25.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:26.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So the guy is giving the girl chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:31.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And wouldn't it be like a girl giving a girl chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If the other person's a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:33.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The other person's a guy in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess it doesn't matter as long as you're having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:44.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I wanna go overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.97,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, yesterday, Miyuki-san was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:54.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Females giving chocolates on \NFebruary 14th is a Japanese custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.92,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.10,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In western society, people of both genders...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:13:00.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...give chocolate and cards \Nto friends and people they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:05.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so a girl like me could still get lots of chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I guess you could interpret it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...but you sure have a lot of confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Like you already know for a fact that you'll be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:13.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In foreign countries, little girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:14.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:16.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No risqué statements allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:18.75,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Will you accept this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Happy Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Here, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Incredible wrapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:25.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...for a uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:28.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And the inside's all cool and heart-shaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:30.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I put some effort into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.14,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's always enthusiastic about this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She was making them until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And it's only friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:40.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't give any friendship chocolate to guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,They'll definitely get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:43.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Anyway, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:48.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami's giving me chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa was making hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:50.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so I just joined in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:51.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:59.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami looking like she's good at everything when she \Nactually sucks so she secretly works hard turns me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:13:59.54,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:00.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shut up and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:02.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:08.84,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.55,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, it's a just friends thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:12.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry the shape's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.24,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The shape isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:21.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What matters is that you made it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,S-Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I told you it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.77,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:27.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:29.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The first time's most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So did you give anybody chocolate, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:36.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I gave chocolate to my father and a relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:40.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I gave chocolate to everybody I'm friendly with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I gave chocolate to you, Tsukasa, and Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:43.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.46,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You guys sure had a boring St. Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:48.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't need to hear it from \Nsomeone who lives in an online game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:50.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Your cousin was accepted to Ryouou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:54.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's pretty far from her home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:58.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so she'll be living with us starting next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She's always been like a little sister anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...so we've been in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:02.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:06.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...nobody would be able to tell who's younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,No, like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.98,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She's like a little sister in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's that small?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:13.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But if she got accepted to our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...your cousin must be really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:18.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That just sounds like you're \Nbeing really presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:18.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Since you're a student here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:22.26,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,But I barely passed the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Exams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking our exams next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll be spending the whole year studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sounds awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:30.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Should I even take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:33.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I haven't even picked a major.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.59,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You seriously need to start thinking about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:40.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Studying, manual labor, and me just don't mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What kind of future do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:46.40,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Use a hobby to make profit and make games...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.40,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I design games. 'Cause it's my hobby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:49.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be a self-proclaimed manga \Nartist who can only sell at Comiket...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:49.11,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Megas smoked cheese-nyoro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:52.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or perhaps, indulge your curiosity\Nand become a professional writer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.61,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}There can only be one truth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.57,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}And this isn't it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:55.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, maybe just a novelist who aims for a niche market.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since you like computers, \NI guess art design might work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:03.25,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe a scenario writer who uses\Nrandom material instead of an actual story writer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.41,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or she doesn't go to college...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:07.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or they're all the same thing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:07.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:12.38,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:13.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Legendary Girl A...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:17.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:22.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She shook us off last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:22.89,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:23.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:23.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:31.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We will absolutely make sure she\Nreaches the goal known as our register!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:32.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Giro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She seems to be at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Then allow us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:39.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...help her find her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:40.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:41.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let 'er rip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:41.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:42.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:42.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:43.45,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:43.83,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:44.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:45.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Aw yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:48.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:52.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Attempting to determine Legendary \NGirl A's objective for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:52.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:53.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Countin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's the newest comic out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:55.92,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:57.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Volume 14 of Sgt. Frog, sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Raise the height of our goods to the appropriate level...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...to bring them to the attention of Legendary Girl A!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.01,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And deploy the flyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Deployment complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.31,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on her movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.94,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And as Legendary Girl A approaches the register...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:14.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...deploy our best-selling goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:15.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:16.82,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:19.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.20,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:24.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Legendary Girl A's objective isn't the comics section!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:27.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:29.79,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Switch target to the DVD section.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:30.67,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:35.34,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...block all side paths so Legendary Girl A...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:36.71,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...heads straight to the new DVD section!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:37.42,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.13,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.39,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Tama! Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:43.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:47.85,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Tama-tama-tama-tama build-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:47.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Gero-gero-gero-gero build-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.19,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.48,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...picked up the item!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.65,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've finally become a winner today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:07.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:09.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let us have a wild celebration tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:10.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.33,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It was a feint!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll have to bring out my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:29.93,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Come...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:34.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Bring that bargain, super-rare, \Nout-of-print DVD to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.11,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.23,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,She is heading for the register.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:39.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.95,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The crowd inside me is \Ncheering with applause right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:47.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:48.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Your total comes to 1,785 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm short 3 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Please put that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.02,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:23.87,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's kick this into gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:29.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We're already on the thirteenth \Nepisode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:30.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:33.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,As you already know, I'm \Nyour navigator, Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:34.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:35.27,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.37,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.50,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.29,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.17,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.44,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.43,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.80,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We're on episode 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}D-D-D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Into the second season.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.21,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:48.76,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's like we've reached the \Nfifth station on Mt. Fuji, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:47.12,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.02,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}D-D-D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:50.22,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.73,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can drive up to the fifth station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:55.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:58.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I've climbed Mt. Takao before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.70,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Don't you have something else to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:01.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.62,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}D-D-D-D-D-D-D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.90,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Man, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama's twin drills look wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.12,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What's so wonderful about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.61,0:20:10.53,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The way they go round and round like a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:13.47,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.66,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.00,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We have a special announcement today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:19.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The results for the Lucky Star figure poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.68,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Let's have Akira-sama announce the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:27.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The characters that will soon \Nbe getting figures are Konata Izumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.01,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Akira-sama, do a proper job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.30,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.35,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, everybody knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.69,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:37.85,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Just means that the higher-ups think the\Nactual show is more important than this corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Of course not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:42.61,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.07,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The producers agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:45.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.32,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'll just fall for your little trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.03,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,I'm already used to being backstabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.78,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Little trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.64,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,That's an awful thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:58.05,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And don't tell me that it says \Nyou're going to have a figure made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:20:59.04,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:20:59.62,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.16,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,We'll be making a figure of Konata Izumi-san this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:04.91,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,And the popular Minoru Shiraishi will also get a figure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,The hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.81,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:11.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,It's time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:16.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,So please send us any suggestions \Nor comments you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:18.60,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You can leave them on our home page.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.52,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Right, Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:21.69,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:21.69,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Er, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.36,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.86,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,B-Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:26.28,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:27.57,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:27.57,ls_alt,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:28.49,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,All the staff members can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:29.15,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,D-Drill!
