Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:08.74,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Comrade, I have a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.99,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Japanese anime is now a global industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.58,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,If we use it to brainwash the people on Pekopon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:16.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,...we can complete the invasion \Nof Pekopon in no time, sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You're a genius, Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:20.08,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:22.54,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,A soldier should act like a soldier and use brute force!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.18,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth, you red dharma doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:28.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In this age, whoever controls \Ninformation controls the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:30.72,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,Well, your prehistoric mind wouldn't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.51,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,You better watch yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:33.01,ls_standard,,0,0,0,,In any case...
